//   7. ordain_airgap       — airgap supply chain: enshrine, forge, enshrine, airgap
//   8. ordain_bind         — bind rbev-bottle-plantuml + propagate to pluml
//   9. ordain_graft        — docker pull + BURE_TWEAK ordain rbev-graft-demo
//
